        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Lee Hong-Ju (Kim So-Hyun) is as an animation production PD. When she was in the 3rd grade of high school student, she fell in love for the first time. She went through a hard breakup and has been skeptical of love since that time. 10 years later, she meets Kang Hu-Young (Chae Jong-Hyeop), who witnessed her miserable past.\n\nKang Hu-Young works as a financial planner and is smart and handsome. He returns to South Korea after 10 years. He meets his first love Lee Hong-Ju as if by chance and fate. He faces a strong wave of emotions. Meanwhile, Bang Joon-Ho (Yun Ji-On), who is a popular novel writer with a free spirit. Lee Hong-Ju is his big fan. Kim Hye-Ji (Kim Da-Som) is Lee Hong-Ju’s best friend and works as an English teacher.",
